videos.description: Iowa State's Hakeem Butler leaps to pull in the touchdown pass from Brock Purdy.
videos.headline: Butler leaps for TD catch

videos.description: Alex Barnes takes the hand off and slips out of a tackle to score a 10-yard Kansas State touchdown.
videos.headline: Barnes slips through for 10-yard TD run

videos.description: Brock Purdy airs it out to Hakeem Butler for a 65-yard reception to the 3-yard line.
videos.headline: Butler goes deep for 65-yard reception

videos.description: Skylar Thompson muscles through the Cyclones defense to score a Wildcat touchdown.
videos.headline: Thompson muscles through with 4-yard TD run

videos.description: Skylar Thompson lofts a pass to the corner of the end zone and Isaiah Zuber tracks it down for the Kansas State touchdown.
videos.headline: Thompson lofts it to Zuber for TD

videos.description: Kevion McGee comes up with an interception on the Brock Purdy deep ball after juggling it and falling over the receiver.
videos.headline: Purdy throws INT on deep pass

videos.description: Skylar Thompson finds Chabastin Taylor running along the back of the end zone and delivers the touchdown pass to put Kansas State up 31-21 over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Thompson connects with Taylor in back of end zone for TD

videos.description: Skylar Thompson fumbles after getting hit in the backfield and the Iowa State defense returns it for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa State defense forces fumble, returns for TD
